# Project

- **Type**: Tauri app
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **UI**: React
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + Framer Motion
- **Components**: Radix UI (accessibility) + custom glass styling
- **Icons**: lucide-react (SF-like)
- **State**: Zustand

## Context

- Desktop app to manage multiple **Klipper** printers via **Moonraker API**.
- **Moonraker HTTP API reference**: [external API docs](https://moonraker.readthedocs.io/en/latest/external_api/).
- **Klipper `printer.cfg` reference** (sections and parameters): [Configuration reference](https://www.klipper3d.org/Config_Reference.html).
- **CAN bus setup, flashing, updates, troubleshooting** (Klipper printers): [Esoterical’s CANBus Guide](https://canbus.esoterical.online/).
- **Primary platform**: **Windows** (main product focus).
- **Release builds** also target **macOS (Apple Silicon)** and **Linux** on **Debian 12+** with **GNOME** (validate UI and packaging there).
- Users add printers by **IP** and **API key**.

